Cubieboard/Cubietruck Gentoo Overlay
====================================

The overlay includes ebuilds for the following packages:

dev-embedded/sunxi-tools
    Homepage:    https://github.com/linux-sunxi/sunxi-tools
    Description: Tools to help hacking Allwinner A10 devices

media-libs/mesa
    Homepage:    http://mesa3d.sourceforge.net/
    Description: OpenGL-like graphic library for Linux

sys-boot/u-boot-sunxi
    Homepage:    https://github.com/linux-sunxi/u-boot-sunxi
    Description: u-boot for Allwinner sunxi series of SoCs (A10, A13, A10s, and A20)

sys-kernel/cubieboard-sources
    Homepage:    https://github.com/cubieboard/linux-sunxi
    Description: Linux source for Allwinner/Boxchip F20 (sun3i), A10 (sun4i) and A12/A13 (sun5i) SoCs

virtual/linux-sources
    Description: Virtual for Linux kernel sources

x11-base/xorg-drivers
    Homepage:    http://www.gentoo.org/
    Description: Meta package containing deps on all xorg drivers

x11-base/xorg-server
    Homepage:    http://xorg.freedesktop.org/
    Description: X.Org X servers

x11-drivers/xf86-video-fbturbo
    Homepage:    https://github.com/ssvb/xf86-video-fbturbo
    Description: Xorg DDX driver for Allwinner A10/A13 and other ARM devices

x11-libs/libdri2
    Homepage:    https://github.com/robclark/libdri2
    Description: DRI2 extension to the X Window System

x11-libs/libvdpau-sunxi
    Homepage:    https://github.com/linux-sunxi/libvdpau-sunxi
    Description: Experimental VDPAU for Allwinner sunxi SoCs

x11-libs/limadriver
    Homepage:    https://gitorious.org/lima/
    Description: Free software graphics driver for the ARM Mali GPUs

x11-libs/sunxi-libump
    Homepage:    https://github.com/linux-sunxi/libump
    Description: Unified Memory Provider (UMP) user-space API

x11-libs/sunxi-mali
    Homepage:    https://github.com/linux-sunxi/sunxi-mali
    Description: Sunxi Mali-400 support libraries
